Package org.vanted.addons.lmme.decomposition

Class PredefinedMMDecomposition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vanted.addons.lmme.decomposition.MMDecompositionAlgorithm
      • org.vanted.addons.lmme.decomposition.PredefinedMMDecomposition
  • public class PredefinedMMDecomposition
extends MMDecompositionAlgorithm
    This method is based on an existing decomposition of the model, which is contained in the underlying SBML file of the model in the form of reaction notes.

    Reactions in this case are required to have assigned the name of the subsystem that they belong to.

    Author:
    Michael Aichem
